{"tid":993114,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解KFC唔出呢款鬆餅？","createTime":"2019-01-23T16:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T06:54:58.000Z","uid":175988,"like":33,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf6b3bd895980be0ad335dd2dc95994067041b0","tid":993114,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"<strong>Whataburger @ Texas</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IB3CcLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIB3CcLR.jpg&h=9151e318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>炸雞鬆餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n鬆餅外脆內綿，帶些少軟糯煙韌口感；蜜糖醬清香唔過甜，減低炸雞膩感；炸雞外皮微酥唔過硬，食落喉嚨好c服<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論：早餐bestseller當之無愧。如果KFC出呢隻早餐(多蜜糖版)嘅話我一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"1e0e6f8176fd6d450760f0232b8d14545f853ebf","tid":993114,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502631dcc09e95abba20c251a7f6259b5b421765","tid":993114,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:29:25.000Z","msg":"咁夾法唔止張住個口，應該吞都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ad8bd69ddd37e33479df8f54125dfd3272876b","tid":993114,"uid":204917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b265e3414beb31515e6fb44c58ebfe2b23b687bf","tid":993114,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"502631dcc09e95abba20c251a7f6259b5b421765","tid":993114,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:29:25.000Z","msg":"咁夾法唔止張住個口，應該吞都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:34:00.000Z",